  "subject": "Initialize dmi-properties for new registrations on 2026-04-23 model",
  "commit_message": "Initialize dmi-properties for new registrations on 2026-04-23 model\n\n- Added ignoreR20260423Model flag to CmHandleRegistrationService to\n  detect when the new yang model is active\n- Initialize dmiProperties to empty string during fresh registration\n  so resolveDmiProperties serializes additionalProperties correctly\n- Added unit test for JsonProcessingException catch block in\n  resolveDmiProperties\n- Made objectMapper field non-final to enable test injection on Java 17\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-3219\n\nChange-Id: I71bd88296d3475a5551803f4902dea39873ebd6d\nSigned-off-by: egernug <gerard.nugent@est.tech>\n",
